n(? (type of zero))               # -> Natural\n```\n\n#### Type Hierarchy Example\n\n```lino\n(Type 0)\n(Type: (Type 0) Type)\n(Boolean: Type Boolean)\n(True: Boolean True)\n(False: Boolean False)\n(? (Boolean of Type))            # -> 1\n(? (True of Boolean))            # -> 1\n```",
